{"tid":328744,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家仲記唔記得你嘅初吻係點發生？","createTime":"2017-07-19T21:46:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T00:38:22.000Z","uid":97947,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c583b16086463aa1a3441b161c8ba2410bba3e4","tid":328744,"uid":97947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T21:46:16.000Z","msg":"我好記得嗰日係我生日，我地同成班朋友飲完酒之後番屋企。咁我就同佢講我送你番屋企啦，但係佢竟然死都唔肯比我送，話我飲醉，仲調番轉頭話佢送我番屋企，咁我見佢咁堅持，唉，好啦，比你送啦<br />\n<br />\n（嗰一刻我已經諗好左，等佢送我到樓下之後我再話我送番你番屋企，就係咁同佢無限輪回成晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n到屋企樓下啦，佢就叫我上樓，而我就企佢隔離賴死唔走，賴左大約兩三分鐘，佢突然捉住我，<span style=\"color: red;\">KISS</span>,我反應唔切呆左係到，之後佢問我，咁而家你肯番屋企未呀？我諗都唔駛諗！未！<br />\n<br />\n除非你KISS多我一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"824081c69304b490505b7196ed2c29a38b07dba2","tid":328744,"uid":601,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T22:29:21.000Z","msg":"有無諗過無人想知"},{"pid":"f2325821370470d8dc966e5872fec247b1343b80","tid":328744,"uid":97947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T22:49:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無諗過無人想知</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2901e491ed753af93321915ca5f0f7d2be528a5","tid":328744,"uid":17611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T22:52:48.000Z","msg":"無人想知"},{"pid":"2b04f80f2fe4fdf24d69acfe8fa4d10ce76c473e","tid":328744,"uid":97947,"lik